name: tabuexp - Campo Minado/Minefield
description:
"Distorted metallic beats to cross minefields"

This track was actually made to be an instrumental at SASKIA's first album, "pq", but was lately discarted. The main beats were made with a original Roland 808 processed through several Boss distortion racks. Some digital instruments appear also in the wobble lead and effects. Everything was composed and recorded at Audio Porto Studio, in Porto Alegre, RS, Brazill, 2018.
